1
00:00:00,562 --> 00:00:04,540
Nigel is our new next-door neighbour.
Nigel是我们新搬来的隔壁邻居.

2
00:00:04,541 --> 00:00:06,616
He's a pilot.
他是个飞行员.

3
00:00:06,617 --> 00:00:09,710
He was in the R. A. F.
他曾在皇家空军任职.

4
00:00:09,711 --> 00:00:13,474
He will fly to New York next month.
下个月他将飞往纽约.

5
00:00:13,492 --> 00:00:18,157
The month after next he'll fly to Tokyo.
再下个月他将飞往东京.

6
00:00:18,158 --> 00:00:21,808
At the moment, he's in Madrid.
现在他在马德里.

7
00:00:21,809 --> 00:00:25,191
He flew to Spain a week ago.
他一星期以前飞到西班牙的.

8
00:00:25,446 --> 00:00:30,225
He'll return to London the week after next.
再下个星期他将返回伦敦.

9
00:00:30,226 --> 00:00:33,910
He's only forty-one years old,
他只有41岁,

10
00:00:34,059 --> 00:00:40,780
and he has already been to nearly every country in the world.
但他却去过世界上几乎每一个国家.

11
00:00:40,781 --> 00:00:44,280
Nigel is a very lucky man.
Nigel是个很幸运的人.

12
00:00:44,301 --> 00:00:50,848
But his wife isn't very lucky. She usually stays at home!
但他的妻子运气不很好.她总是呆在家里!

